data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER** All offers will be reviewed.    WATERFRONT pool home (heated with spa jets). Home is only 3 years old!  This stunning home is an absolute gem, boasting upgraded features and appliances that are sure to impress. A spacious layout comprising of 5 bedrooms, an office/den and 3 bathrooms, this home offers ample space for all or those who love to entertain.  Whether you're looking for an office space or a versatile flex area, this home has you covered!    The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. One of the highlights of this home is the heated salt water pool with spa overlooking a beautiful water view, perfect for enjoying a refreshing swim or simply relaxing poolside while taking in the breathtaking scenery.      In addition to its stunning features, this home is ideally located in sought after South Lakeland! The community offer 2 resort style pools, playgrounds, walking paths, dog park and fitness area. Enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities, including shopping centers and community parks. Shopping, movies, and entertainment plaza located within 7 miles of community.  Call or text for a showing!
